ActEmergency Management Act
SubjectProvincial Emergency Financial Assistance Order No. 231, Manitoba
PrecisPROVINCIAL EMERGENCY FINANCIAL ASSISTANCE ORDER NO. 231 which makes a declaration of federal concern and authorizes the provision of financial assistance to the province of MANITOBA, with respect to the severe snowstorm and freezing rain that occurred from October 8 to 12, 2019.
